🍕 Common Specialty Combinations (For Reference)

These aren’t individual toppings you select separately, but they show how toppings are grouped on named pizzas: 
Slice Pizzeria

Supreme: pepperoni, seasoned pork, beef, mushrooms, green peppers, onions
Meat Lover’s: pepperoni, Italian sausage, ham, bacon, pork, beef
Veggie Lover’s: mushrooms, onions, green peppers, tomatoes, black olives
Backyard BBQ Chicken: grilled chicken + bacon + onions
Hawaiian/Hawaiian Chicken: ham + pineapple (+ chicken/green peppers)
Buffalo Chicken: buffalo sauce base + chicken + onions + banana peppers
